sentences.english: Corellon Unaligned Arcane magic, spring, beauty, the arts.
sentences.chinese: 科瑞隆無陣營奧法，春季，美貌，藝術。

sentences.english: Bladeling PCs may be any non-chaotic alignment.
sentences.chinese: 刀鋒怪玩家可以成爲任何非混亂陣營。

sentences.english: India and Brazil are both also wooed by the Zionist camp.
sentences.chinese: 印度和巴西都被猶太復國主義陣營所支持。
寇德無陣營風暴，強壯，戰鬥。

sentences.english: Same faction players in stealth are seeable by any other player of that faction.
sentences.chinese: 潛行玩家對同陣營的其他玩家可見。

sentences.english: The Ahmadinejad camp won the largest share of seats in the Majlis, or parliament.
sentences.chinese: 艾哈邁迪內賈德陣營在議會選舉中贏得了最多的席位。

sentences.english: Many in the opposition viewed it as an attempted power grab by the military.
sentences.chinese: 反對黨陣營中的很多人都將之視爲軍方企圖奪權。

sentences.english: First, the Cold War split the membership along East-West lines.
sentences.chinese: 首先，冷戰以東西方劃線將成員國分裂成兩大陣營。

sentences.english: This is the policy favoured by tha antinuclear camp.
sentences.chinese: 這項政策得到了反核陣營的支持。

sentences.english: Several friends and I am a good camp, they divided into two areas.
sentences.chinese: 我和朋友幾個分好了陣營，便劃分了兩個地方。

sentences.english: The paladin looked up, cued to his peril only by the dark hordes themselves pulling back with Judith's arrival.
sentences.chinese: 聖騎士在黑暗陣營自動退卻時才發現茱蒂絲的危險性。

sentences.english: At the root of the deficiency is the modern-day habit of shunning the sun, says the pro-vitamin D camp.
sentences.chinese: 維生素原D陣營說缺乏根是現代太陽照射的習性。

sentences.english: So if you play a human paladin, you'd only be able to change to a blood elf paladin.
sentences.chinese: 比如說一個人類聖騎，在轉換陣營後只能選擇血精靈。

sentences.english: Added a "gain 1000 denars" in camp cheat menu.
sentences.chinese: 增加了一個“獲得1000第納爾”的陣營作弊菜單。

sentences.english: Western commentators on China fall into two main camps.
sentences.chinese: 西方的中國評論家們分爲兩個陣營。

sentences.english: There were no comparable gestures from the other side.
sentences.chinese: 另一個陣營方面卻沒有相應的姿態。
